      <odd id="aspace_e666ae5444df324e9c288169603cd107">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>The collection was formerly known as the Kohut Girl's School Records (MS 956). With subsequent additions, Kohut family material now predominates and the title of the collection was changed to reflect this in 2009.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_4ef746e22a625fb75d3ccecb8e562055">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>Transferred from the stacks of Sterling Memorial Library, 1942; transferred from the Judaica Collection Curator, 2001, 2007, and 2009.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <custodhist id="aspace_71377217a102596352b8744a12007f55">
